These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, golf, basketball, swimming
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is golf and the person drinking milk##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking mirinda##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk         | milk   | iced-tea | mirinda       |
| Sport      | swimming | rugby | basketball   | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, singing, baking, board-games
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, mexican, american, japanese
1. the japanese is between the person who's hobby is baking and the mexican##2
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
3. the american is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking | baking | board-games |
| Nationality   | mexican    | japanese   | pakistani | american       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, cucumber, watermelon, raspberry
There are 4 different nationalities: american, polish, thai, malaysian
1. the thai is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the thai is between the polish and the person eating cucumber##2
3. the polish is on the far left##1
4. the malaysian is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
5. the person eating cucumber is the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | raspberry    | peas | cucumber   | watermelon  |
| Nationality   | polish | thai   | malaysian | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, horse, guinea-pig, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, ice-hockey, sailing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the frog is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rabbit   | frog    | guinea-pig       | horse   |
| Sport   | sailing | volleyball | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, milk, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, board-games, gardening, sudoku
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking tea is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is board-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade        | milk | tea  | almond-milk |
| Hobby      | gardening | board-games  | sudoku | fishing    |

