.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, house, gospel, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, tennis, lacrosse, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the fan of techno is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
4. the fan of house is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the fan of gospel is between the fan of disco and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | house     | gospel           | disco | techno  |
| Sport         | weightlifting | ice-hockey | tennis   | lacrosse |

