.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, soul, techno, metal
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, subway, trike, skateboard
1. the fan of soul is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the fan of rock##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the fan of rock is between the person driving the tram and the fan of techno##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | soul | rock | techno      |
| Transport     | trike | tram    | subway  | skateboard |

