.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, baseball, basketball, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, airplane, train, car
1. the person driving the bus is the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person driving the train##2
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | rugby | snowboarding | basketball     | baseball   |
| Transport   | train   | airplane     | car | bus |

