.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pomegranate, kiwi, lime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, climbing, surfing
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person eating lime##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person eating pomegranate and the person who's sport is surfing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | lime   | kiwi      | pomegranate   | mango  |
| Sport   | surfing | cycling | climbing | badminton |

