.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, orange, mango, corn
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, western, epic, mystery
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person eating orange is between the person eating corn and the person eating kiwi##2
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | kiwi     | orange | corn   | mango        |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | epic   | western | mystery |

