.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, collecting, hiking, card-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, folk, jazz, reggae
1. the fan of jazz is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
3. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is the fan of folk##1
5. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the fan of folk is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is card-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | hiking | card-games | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | jazz          | folk     | reggae  | country     |

