4. the electrician is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | electrician | firefighter | bartender | videographer     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific   | drama    | disaster   | crime |

