2. the colombian is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the polish is between the person driving the taxi and the spanish##2
4. the colombian is on the right of the polish##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | spanish | polish | colombian |
| Transport     | train     | jet-ski   | van | taxi  |

