3. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the turtle and the indonesian##2
4. the owner of the rat is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | indian | indonesian | chinese | malaysian |
| Pet           | hamster  | rat  | horse | turtle      |

