.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, collecting, skydiving, traveling
4 different pets are kept: snake, mouse, horse, goldfish
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the owner of the snake and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | skydiving    | traveling     | drawing | collecting |
| Pet     | mouse | goldfish | horse       | snake     |

 